videos.headline: Wake Forest scores twice in four minutes to kick off ACC battle
videos.description: First, Sam Hartman fires a long pass to A.T. Perry for an early 40-yard touchdown. Then on the next possession, Hartman connects with Jaquarii Roberson for a 49-yard gain, setting up Kenneth Walker III's short TD.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wake Forest scores twice in four minutes to kick off ACC battle) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wake Forest regains the lead with 75-yard touchdown
videos.description: Kenneth Walker III scores his second touchdown of the day, rushing 75 yards to the house to put Wake Forest back up on top vs. Virginia.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wake Forest regains the lead with 75-yard touchdown) 2020/10/17 ESHEET
